<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_87" id="43r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_87_r3l2"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Eglolfſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> cʒü Pernfels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_87_r3l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns vnd auch den Scheppfen bey vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l4">von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> küeblin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Darvmb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ſie beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l6">vnd cʒe rede geſacʒt / . vnd die hat 
<add><ab facs="#facs_87_r3l5">vns </ab></add> geantwurt / daʒ Jr ir etwiuil ſchuldig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l7">ſeit / des Jr ir in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Gerichts püch bekant habt / vnd darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l8">ſie auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> Jnſıgel / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / . den ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l9">vns auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> laſſen hat / . vnd ſprichet / Jr ſolt Jr die langſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l10">becʒalt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Jr Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex></expan></del> biſher <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / . vnd cʒieh ſıch die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l12">klage in des Gerichts püch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_87_r3l11">nu gen dem Jare </ab></add> / daʒ ſıe die <expan>v<ex>er</ex>newen</expan> müſʒ / darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l13">ſie ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan> hab / . vnd vns dunkt ſelcʒeim / daʒ Jr v̈ber das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l14">in ſölıcher maʒʒ herein ſchreıbt / . vnd mainen wes Jr bekant vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l15"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / daʒ vnſer <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>gerin</expan> müglıch dabey beleıb / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_87_r3l16"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria <expan>S<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſcere $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_87" id="43r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglolfst<ex>ein</ex></expan> czü Pernfels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns und auch den scheppfen bey uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Küeblin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>. Darumb
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir sie besant und cze rede gesaczt
                        und die hat <add>uns</add> geantwurt, daz ir ir etwivil schuldig seit, des
                        ir ir in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gerichts püch bekant habt und darumb
                        sie auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief mit
                            <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> insigel und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, den sie uns auch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> lassen hat; und sprichet, ir solt ir
                        die langst beczalt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir ir bisher
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan> habt; und czieh sich die
                        klage in des gerichts püch <add>nu gen dem jare</add>, daz sie die
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>newen</expan> müsz, darumb sie ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan> hab; und uns dunkt selczeim, daz ir
                        über das in sölicher mazz herein schreibt, und mainen, wes ir bekant und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt, daz unser <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>gerin</expan> müglich dabey beleib.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria
                            <expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> remi<ex>ni</ex>scere.</ab>
</div>
